Vesicomyidae 
<bibRefCitation author="Dall" box="[423,696,1767,1793]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" refString="Dall, W. H. &amp; Simpson, C. T. (1901) The Mollusca of Porto Rico. United States Fish Commission Bulletin, 20, 351 - 524." type="journal article" year="1901">Dall &amp; Simpson, 1901</bibRefCitation>
